[FULL CAST]
Clover Clips!

401
00:23:19,055 --> 00:23:20,682
[GREY]
"Today's the Day."

402
00:23:22,225 --> 00:23:24,644
[GAUCHE]
Marie.

403
00:23:24,728 --> 00:23:26,354
[GREY]
Today's the day.

404
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:33,361
[GREY] I'm going to thank
him for what he did.

405
00:23:33,445 --> 00:23:34,362
Hey.

406
00:23:34,446 --> 00:23:36,656
[yelps]

407
00:23:36,740 --> 00:23:38,116
[GREY]
Today's the day.

408
00:23:38,199 --> 00:23:40,326
Look. Isn't she the cutest?

409
00:23:40,410 --> 00:23:41,494
[GREY]
Today's the day.

410
00:23:41,578 --> 00:23:43,163
So cute it hurts.

411
00:23:43,246 --> 00:23:44,581
[GREY]
Today's the day.

412
00:23:44,664 --> 00:23:45,707
Cute, right?

413
00:23:45,790 --> 00:23:46,833
[GREY]
Today's the day.

414
00:23:46,916 --> 00:23:48,251
Cute, right?

415
00:23:48,335 --> 00:23:50,920
[VANESSA] They seem to be
doing that a lot lately.

416
00:23:51,004 --> 00:23:52,339
I wonder what it's about.

417
00:23:52,422 --> 00:23:54,507
Nice communication, guys.

418
00:23:56,843 --> 00:23:58,345
[LUCK]
That was awesome!

419
00:23:58,428 --> 00:24:00,221
I wonder what everyone
else is up to.

420
00:24:00,305 --> 00:24:02,932
If they don't hurry, I'll
beat everyone here myself.

421
00:24:03,016 --> 00:24:07,812
